726176f-a.title: Queens: Borden Avenue - 21st Street
726176f-a.text:
Borden Avenue, north side, west from near 21st
Street, showlng a general view of the area across
which was later constructed the elevated highway,
carrying traffic to and from the entrance to the
Oueens-Midtown Tunnel, a few blocks away.
